## 🧾 Story: EIS Consent Read API Integration

### Objective
Implement method to call EIS Consent Read API and fetch consent status.

---

### External API
POST /eis/consent/read

---

### Request
{
  "touchPointId": "MIF",
  "dpData": {
    "dpMobile": "9999999999",
    "dpCIF": "mobile+MID"
  }
}

---

### Response
{
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "consentStatus": "ACTIVE"
}

---

### Development Steps
1. Create service class: CcmsIntegrationService
2. Add method:
   boolean checkConsentFromCCMS(ConsentCheckRequest request)
3. Build request payload
4. Encrypt payload (AES)
5. Call EIS API (RestTemplate/WebClient)
6. Decrypt response
7. Parse consentStatus
8. Return boolean

---

### Acceptance Criteria
- API call works successfully
- Returns correct consent status
- Handles timeout and exceptions


